welcome_message_body: Welcome to Fountain Valley, where the sun is always shining and the community is full of charm. Known for its beautiful parks and friendly locals, we invite you to explore and enjoy all that our city has to offer.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Municipal Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Municipal Airport handles all freight and cargo shipments.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Long Beach Municipal Airport serves all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: North Terminal
terminals.description: The North Terminal at Long Beach Municipal Airport serves all domestic flights operated by JetBlue and Southwest Airlines.

terminals.name: South Terminal
terminals.description: The South Terminal at Long Beach Municipal Airport serves all international flights and some domestic flights operated by Delta Air Lines.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's free WiFi network by selecting 'LGB Free WiFi' on their device and agreeing to the terms and conditions.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Compton Airport serves commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Compton Airport caters to private jet and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal serves all domestic and international flights at Chino Airport.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at El Monte Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at El Monte Airport caters to private and chartered flights only.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Tom Bradley International Terminal
terminals.description: The largest and most modern terminal at LAX, serving international flights.
